Package au.edu.rmit.tzar.resultscopier

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ResultsCopier
    Copies results from local storage to permanent storage.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncResultsCopier
    ResultsCopier decorator which accepts copy requests and adds them to a threadsafe queue.
    CopierFactory
    Creates Results copiers with certain characteristics.
    DbUpdatingResultsCopier
    A ResultsCopier wrapper which also updates the runs database.
    FileResultsCopier
    Copies results using the local file system (including mounted remote drives).
    NoopCopier
    No-op results copier.
    RetryingResultsCopier
    Decorator for ResultsCopiers that retries failed copy attempts.
    ScpResultsCopier
    Copies results using scp.
    SshClientFactory
    Spawns new SSHClients.
    SshClientFactoryKeyAuth
    Creates SSHClients using pemfile authentication.
    SshClientFactoryPasswordAuth
    Creates SSHClients using password authentication.
